{"tid":2335375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粵港簽東江水新協議　未來3年斥逾$147億買水貴2.5%　可按輸入量減水價","createTime":"2020-12-21T23:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T02:47:43.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1202eda82f762b5e2c7408e65f6aa90a13027f5a","tid":2335375,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gsMb1e34xOPXi7Kbg21ZQH9eqzM=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K5XCTWYQLNDZJCC2KOPRQD4SOY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgsMb1e34xOPXi7Kbg21ZQH9eqzM%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK5XCTWYQLNDZJCC2KOPRQD4SOY.png&h=ae70f68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港府與廣東省簽訂新一份購買東江水協議，未來3年港府共斥資147.87億元買水，較上一份3年合約144.21億元貴2.5%。資料圖片<br />\n...<br />\n港府與廣東省簽訂新一份購買東江水協議，未來3年港府共斥資147.87億元買水，較上一份3年合約144.21億元貴2.5%。目前新一份協議首次採用「統包扣減」方式買水，可按減少輸入東江水量而扣減水價。另外，由於疫情關係，明年實際水價將凍結在2020年水平。<br />\n<br />\n根據發展局向立法會提交的文件顯示，是次政府與廣東省簽訂的新協議，將首次採用「統包扣減」方式買水。政府稱這是一個優化「統包總額」的新方式，可按減少輸入東江水量而扣減水價。過往15年所簽訂的五份東江水供水協議，均採用「統包總額」方式供水，無論實際東江水供水量是多少，總額水價都是固定。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/URTKC5Z3UFFFLFK7QK7MNQK4LA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FURTKC5Z3UFFFLFK7QK7MNQK4LA%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=83d7f68d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FURTKC5Z3UFFFLFK7QK7MNQK4LA%2F&h=0f5b0122\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/URTKC5Z3UFFFLFK7QK7MNQK4LA/</a>"},{"pid":"32ea39ccae3714e03e5434fefdc5bc8636297e46","tid":2335375,"uid":153827,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T00:13:37.000Z","msg":"肯起海水化淡廠未，唔想再飲有毒廢水...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/d